precis:
Authority to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Government of Jamaica
respecting the consolidation and rescheduling of principal and interest
payable on certain loans in a manner that is consistent with the Agreed
Minute on the Consolidation of the Debt of Jamaica done at Paris on
January 25, 1993.
